Overview
========

This was the DNSandMX administration application that users use to configure
their domains.

It allows them to manage DNS (Primary or Secondary) for their domains. As well
as set up Backup Mail Exchangers or Mail Forwarding for their domains, whoever
they use to manage their DNS.

It is built on top of, PowerDNS, Postfix, MySQL and more...

The application itself is a FastCGI application written in C.

See docs/INSTALL for a somewhat terse getting started guide.

